                "Use when runs were created outside Studio, when only a subset of splits "
                "should be combined, or when you need precise manual control over which "
                "files to include.\n\n"
                "You are responsible for ensuring all selected files share the same physical "
                "setup (geometry, materials, source configuration, and scoring detectors). "
                "No compatibility check is performed on manual selections."
